6:
Hey, you two, check it out! I'm finally
making it big—like, superstar level of
celeb!
10:
C-calm down. What are you talking
about?
16:
My extremeboard trick video! It's
trending all over the place! And look
at those views! Over a million of
them!
19:
All I had to do was film myself and
upload it, just like my new manager
said!
21:
I knew I'd be a hit, but I never knew it
would happen so fast! I'm so good
it's almost scary!
26:
I-I see... Does this mean you are now
a famous person?
32:
You bet! Even the big-time boarders
are liking my video... Look, they're
even talking about me on the news!
I'm breaking the internet!
37:
That's great, Axem! Sounds like this
calls for a celebration.
42:
Hehe, thanks, dude, but it'll have to
wait!
46:
My manager just called me for a
meeting. I'm headed over to
AltExtreme right now.
51:
AltExtreme... Wait, that name... Are
they—
55:
Yup! They're an AltMeme subsidiary!
They manage a ton of pro
extremeboarders!
59:
And I'm about to be one of them!
Get ready to see me in the news
even more! See ya later!
64:
AltMeme... Companies related to
them tend to be pretty sketchy...
68:
We can't just jump to conclusions
either though... Perhaps we should
ask around?
74:
Aw man, I can't believe my
professional debut is finally
happening!
76:
Heh, congratulations, Axem. I look
forward to seeing what else we'll
accomplish together.
79:
Now then, on to business. I'd like to
explain how your debut is going to
play out.
81:
This book contains a list of all the
events you'll be participating in and
who will be winning each one.
Everything's already decided, so just
act your part.
87:
That's certainly one way to look at it,
but where else are you going to get
such an enticing offer? All the fame
and fortune you want, with a
fraction of the work.
90:
And in return, I become your
puppet...
93:
Call it whatever you like, but this is
how things work in the real world. It's
time to grow up and face the music,
Axem.
100:
I want to be a REAL extremeboarder!
No way am I gonna be lumped in
with a bunch of cheats and fakers!
103:
It seems you misunderstood me,
Axem. We have already invested a
large sum into promoting you. You
can't back out so easily.
121:
Dude, your timing was spot-on!
How'd you know to find me?
124:
Let's just say we have a very
informative friend over at Noxel.
127:
When we told her about your
meeting with AltExtreme, she told us
all about their shady dealings. After
that, we rushed over as fast as we
could.
131:
I see no pursuers. That must be her
doing as well.
134:
Gotcha... Thanks, man, I really owe
you one.
141:
Still, I'm sorry about what happened.
This was your chance to make it as
a pro...
146:
Pfft, you call that being a pro?! I'd
just be their lackey! Hard pass!
148:
I'm not gonna follow the path
someone laid out for me. I wanna
shred my own!
152:
Are you sure? I thought becoming a
professional was your dream...
156:
Yeah, and? I never said I was giving
up!
159:
I just have to keep doing what I do
best—skate! And now I know better
than to get tricked by those phonies!
163:
You saw how much I was trending,
right? Now the world knows who I
am, and the ad revenue was pretty
sweet too! Everything worked out
GREAT for me!
168:
Well, I'm glad you're taking
everything in stride...
171:
But I agree... Being able to skate
freely suits you best.
174:
Right? Hehe, I'm gonna skate my
way to the top!
177:
And for everyone's information, I am
now seeking new management!
